---
import image from "../../public/images/jamilSinnoBrush.svg";
import resume from "../../public/JamilSinnoresume.pdf";
---

<div>
    <h4>
        <img src={image} alt="Jamil Sinno's Hero image. The words are Jamil Sinno with a brush stroke in the back. The word Sinno is in between carats which is supposed to make it look like a component. The theme of the logo is an 8 bit design.">
    </h4>
    <section>
        <h1>I enjoy <a class="link" href="https://github.com/jamilsinno" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">writing code</a>, <a class="link" href="https://1drv.ms/x/s!AkPXqkA8Qy8miULhLB_qMRzfvRFB?e=VdvnT5" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">lifting weights</a>, and <a class="link" href="https://linktr.ee/sinnotech" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">creating content</a>.</h1>
        <p class="container">I am a Full-Stack Software Developer specializing in the MERN stack. My career vision is to educate, and advocate for accessibility and representation in tech.</p>
        <a id="resume" href={resume} target="_blank">My Resume</a>
    </section>
</div>

<style>
    div{
        width: auto;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

    h4 img{
        width: 100%;
        max-height: 100%;
    }

    section{
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

	.container {
		margin: 1rem 0;
        border: 1px solid rgba(186, 55, 47, 0.5); 
		background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
        padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: 0.7rem;
	}

    #resume{
		background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
        padding: 1rem;
        font-size: 1.7rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(186, 55, 47, 0.5); 
        border-radius: 0.7em;
    }

    #resume:hover{
        background-color: rgba(186, 55, 47, 0.5); 
        color: #fff;
        border: 1px solid #000;
    }

    #resume:active{
        transform: scale(0.9);
    }

    h1{
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 0.5rem 0;
    }

    section p {
        font-size: 2.0rem;
    }

    .link{
        color: #ba372f;
    }

    @media (min-width: 981px) {
        h4 img{
            justify-self: flex-end;
        }
    }

</style>